 [FILES] Air Commodore Ibikunle Daramola, NAF Director of Public Relations and Information  The Director of Public Relations and Information, NAF Headquarters, AVM Ibikunle Daramola, announced this in a statement on Sunday in Abuja. According to the statement, first responders are at the scene, but sadly, all the seven personnel on board died in the crash. The Chief of Air Staff (CAS), AVM Oladayo Amao, has ordered an immediate investigation into the incident. Amao was quoted as urging the general public to remain calm and await the outcome of the investigation. “CAS, on behalf of all NAF personnel, commiserated with the families of the deceased,’’ Daramola stated.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .